title: Poparazzi
description:
The Poparazzi is a women’s specific, mountain-twin shape with a medium flex; a lively rockered performer for women who want true-to- form, all-mountain fun; cruise the groomers, lap the park, explore the trees - the highly approachable Poparazzi is all about value and independence in the face of preconceptions.
To learn more about the Poparazzi visit: arborcollective.com/snow/boards/view/48/poparazzi-
